Setup
    Step 1
    open Terminal
        Enter 
            sudo visudo
        At the end of the file paste 
            username ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD:ALL
        Save and exit 

    Step 2  (** Info Creates a Virtual Environment venv)
    Open Terminal
        From the /ScenePlay directory
        Enter
            ./requirements.sh
        
    Step 3  (** Info Command Activates the Virtual Environment venv)
        Enter
            ./startApp.sh
         
    Step 4
        In Browser 
            type http://<serverIP>:8086

    repeat Step3-4 for the future app use.